Package: vntrGenotyping
Type: Package
Title: VNTR Read-Count and Density-Ratio Genotyping
Version: 0.1.0
Description: R wrapper around the vntr_genotyping Python package. Counts reads
    overlapping VNTR regions from BAM/CRAM files and returns normalized density
    ratios or raw read counts as a data frame. Requires reticulate and the
    vntr_genotyping Python package.
Imports:
    reticulate
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.0.0
License: MIT + file LICENSE
